<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.6.4">
<l>tāṉāka niṉaiyāṉēl taṉṉiṉaintu naivēṟkōr</l>
<l>mīṉāya koṭineṭuvēḷ valiceyya melivēṉō</l>
<l>tēṉvāya varivaṇṭē tiruvāli nakarāḷum</l>
<l>āṉāyaṟ keṉṉuṟunō yaṟiyacceṉ ṟuraiyāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If he doesn’t think [of me] on his own, when cruel Kāma,</l>
<l rend="indent">on whose banner is a fish,</l>
<l>Creates pain for me, who languishes thinking of him, don’t I grow thin?</l>
<l>Striped bee with honeyed lips, going to the cowherder</l>
<l rend="indent">who rules the city of sacred Āli,</l>
<l>Speak [to him] so he knows of my love sickness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
